g.text: Lysonir has powerful Supportiveagainst bacterial infection:by the important role of Lysozymes and bacteriocins which reduce the overall bacterial load and prevent infections toimprove poultry fock health.
Lysonir has synergistic efect with Antibiotics:When injected with antimicrobial agent to reduce pathogen loads for efective treatment program in poultry focks.
Lysonir has efective Antiviral action:as Lysozyme inhibit the virus replication and decrease the epidemiological pressure in poultry farms and decrease the viral load.

Lysonir improves overall immunity and acting asimmune modulator:referring to soluble Mannan and Beta-Glucan. They stimulate the birds innate immunity to reduce the bad efect of the infection which refect on high fock performance.
